@startuml
title 酒店下单及支付系统协作图

actor 客户
participant "前端应用" as Frontend
participant "API网关" as Gateway
participant "订单服务" as OrderService
participant "房态服务" as RoomService
participant "支付服务" as PaymentService
participant "通知服务" as NotificationService
database "数据库集群" as DB
queue "消息队列" as MQ

== 下单流程 ==

客户 -> Frontend : 1: 选择酒店房型\n填写入住信息
Frontend -> Gateway : 2: 提交订单请求
Gateway -> RoomService : 3: 验证并锁定库存
RoomService -> DB : 4: 执行库存锁定
RoomService --> Gateway : 5: 返回锁定结果

Gateway -> OrderService : 6: 生成订单
OrderService -> DB : 7: 创建订单记录
OrderService --> Gateway : 8: 返回订单详情
Gateway --> Frontend : 9: 显示订单页面
Frontend --> 客户 : 10: 显示支付页面

== 支付流程 ==

客户 -> Frontend : 11: 选择支付方式\n确认支付
Frontend -> Gateway : 12: 提交支付请求
Gateway -> PaymentService : 13: 生成支付请求
PaymentService -> DB : 14: 记录支付流水
PaymentService --> Gateway : 15: 返回支付参数
Gateway --> Frontend : 16: 返回支付页面
Frontend --> 客户 : 17: 跳转支付页面

客户 -> PaymentService : 18: 完成支付验证
PaymentService -> OrderService : 19: 更新订单状态
OrderService -> DB : 20: 更新订单为已支付
OrderService -> RoomService : 21: 确认库存占用
RoomService -> DB : 22: 更新房态状态

OrderService -> NotificationService : 23: 发送通知请求
NotificationService -> MQ : 24: 异步发送消息
NotificationService -> 客户 : 25: 发送确认通知
NotificationService -> DB : 26: 记录通知日志

Frontend --> 客户 : 27: 显示支付成功页面

@enduml